## Approach
Each time, we take the least of multiple of 2, 3, 5 and keep generating from the already-bulit array, thus ensuring the number is always ugly.
![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/da9be94a-e226-4a27-8978-92d8d0923342_1593877426.4611287.png)

## Complexity Analysis
Time: O(N)
Space: O(N)

