use "count" to track player identity, even number is player 1, odd number is player2.
use "bitmap" to track used number, standard technique that has been explained well by others

DP returns if Player1 has a way to win regardless Player 2's action

so at Player 1's turn, if any next state returns true, the current sate returns true. 
at Player 2's turn, only returning true when all of the next state return true. This means no matter how player 2 acts, in the next turn Player 1 has a way to force to win.

